  m_Name: Tiresias
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  EventText: "The blind prophet sits surrounded by bushes near a bubbling spring,
    where he looks unseeing towards the water. Years ago, he stumbled upon Athena
    bathing in the spring ahead. Unfortunately to see a God\u2019s true form is to
    be blinded. Out of pity, she gave him great foresight in exchange. Now he finds
    his attention divided."
  BackgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bbc87c2af7548f74ebe863eb74e2583f, type: 3}
